      "title": "Answering your questions",
      "subtitle": "Got more questions? Send us your enquiry below.",
      "cta": "Get in touch",
      "items": {
        "q1": {
          "question": "What type of affiliates is Adecos AI built for?",
          "answer": "Adecos AI is designed for performance marketers running search, shopping, and native campaigns who need a clear view of ROAS, winners, and wasted spend."
        },
        "q2": {
          "question": "How does Adecos AI connect to my data?",
          "answer": "We connect via secure APIs and data exports from your ad platforms and affiliate networks, then normalize everything into one analytics view."
        },
        "q3": {
          "question": "Do I need a data team to use it?",
          "answer": "No. Adecos AI is built so media buyers and marketers can ask questions in plain language and get insights without writing SQL or building dashboards."
        },
        "q4": {
          "question": "Can I start with just one account or program?",
          "answer": "Yes. You can begin with a single account or program, validate results, then expand to more brands and channels over time."
        },
        "q5": {
          "question": "How quickly can I see value?",
          "answer": "Most teams see useful insights and cleaner reporting within the first week once their data sources are connected."
        }
      }
    },
