        "title": "4. Acceptable Use Policy",
        "content": "You agree to use our Service exclusively for lawful performance marketing and advertising activities. You explicitly agree NOT to: (a) reverse engineer, decompile, or attempt to extract the source code or AI models of Adecos; (b) use our Service to generate explicitly deceptive, malicious, or illegal advertising campaigns; (c) engage in automated scraping, data mining, or extraction of our proprietary databases; (d) intentionally overload or disrupt the integrity and performance of our infrastructure."
      },
      "s5": {
        "title": "5. Intellectual Property Rights",
        "content": "All proprietary materials, including but not limited to the software architecture, Large Language Model configurations, generative algorithms, user interface ('UI'), visual aesthetic designs, dashboards, trademarks, and documentation ('Intellectual Property') are exclusively owned by Adecos. You are granted a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, and revocable license to utilize the Service for its intended operational purpose. No intellectual property rights are ever transferred to you."
      },
      "s6": {
        "title": "6. Disclaimers Regarding AI and Affiliate Marketing",
        "content": "Adecos utilizes probabilistic Artificial Intelligence models to generate insights, research, and campaign recommendations. DUE TO THE NATURE OF AI CONSTRUCTS, WE DO NOT GUARANTEE THE ABSOLUTE ACCURACY, RELIABILITY, OR FACTUAL CORRECTNESS OF OUTPUT PRODUCED BY THE SYSTEM. Furthermore, we explicitly disclaim any guarantees related to financial returns, conversion rates (CVR), Return on Ad Spend (ROAS), or affiliate marketing success. All business decisions made using Adecos data are made entirely upon your own judgement and risk baseline."
      },
      "s7": {
        "title": "7. Limitation of Liability",
        "content": "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, IN NO EVENT SHALL ADECOS, ITS AFFILIATES, DIRECTORS, EMPLOYEES, OR AGENTS BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, PUNITIVE, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR EXEMPLARY DAMAGES. This includes, without limitation, damages for loss of profits, goodwill, data, or other intangible losses arising out of or relating to the use of, or inability to use, the platform and its generated insights. Under no circumstances will total liability exceed the amounts paid by you to Adecos in the previous three (3) months."
      },
